ocieties.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aEnglish languagexDialectsxLexicology. 0aEnglish languagexDialectszEnglandzEast Midlands. 0aEnglish languagexVariationzEnglandzEast Midlands. 4aLanguage & Linguistics. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022 Englishz978311099370708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022z9783110993684oZDB-23-DSP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEdinburgh University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z97831107803900 cprintz978147445554140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978147445556540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781474455565423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781474455565/original  a978-3-11-078039-0  Edinburgh University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099370-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DSPb2022